dmca.title: DMCA notice to chilling effects/google
dmca.body: I gather you reported kabayan central to google for child pornography---is that true? I have ordered from them for years and have never seen such content ontheir site---on the contrary, they are the world's largest site for cultural content from the Phillipines. I lived their as a boy and treasure the excellent selection of books, films, movies, etc. ---If somehow "immoral" content was found to be on the site this must be a "technical" inference (i.e. because maybe some actor(s) in a film were younger than U,S, standards---I don't know...In any case Kebayan is certainly not a porno site so I would urge you to reconsider this action if indeed that's what you've done. Sincerely, Joe Rodgers, BPT.,CT USA
